---
import Layout from '../../../layouts/Layout.astro';
import { getDocBySlug } from '../../../data/navigation';

const doc = getDocBySlug('network-config');

if (!doc) {
	throw new Error('Network config doc metadata is missing');
}
---

<Layout title={`${doc.title} | 通俗版 Claude Code 文档`} description={doc.summary} pathname={doc.path}>
	<article class="space-y-8">
		<header class="card rounded-[32px] p-8 shadow-card">
			<p class="text-sm font-semibold uppercase tracking-[0.24em]" style="color: var(--muted);">Deployment</p>
			<h1 class="mt-3 font-display text-4xl font-semibold">Network config 企业网络配置</h1>
			<p class="mt-4 max-w-3xl text-lg leading-8">{doc.summary}</p>
			<p class="mt-4 max-w-4xl leading-8" style="color: var(--muted);">
				原页来源：
				<a href="https://code.claude.com/docs/en/network-config" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer" class="underline decoration-dotted underline-offset-4">官方 Network config</a>
			</p>
		</header>

		<section class="card rounded-[32px] p-8 shadow-card">
			<h2 class="font-display text-2xl font-semibold">一句人话</h2>
			<div class="mt-4 space-y-4 leading-8">
				<p>大公司通常有代理服务器、防火墙、出网限制。这一页讲怎么在这些环境下配置 Claude Code，让它能正常联网。</p>
			</div>
		</section>

		<section class="card rounded-[32px] p-8 shadow-card">
			<h2 class="font-display text-2xl font-semibold">配置企业代理</h2>
			<div class="mt-4 space-y-4 leading-8">
				<p>如果公司要求所有出网流量走代理，设置环境变量：</p>
				<div class="mt-4 rounded-[24px] border p-6 font-mono text-sm overflow-x-auto" style="border-color: var(--line); background: var(--panel-strong);">
<pre># 在 ~/.zshrc 或 ~/.bashrc 里添加
export HTTPS_PROXY=https://proxy.example.com:8080
export HTTP_PROXY=http://proxy.example.com:8080

# 如果代理需要认证
export HTTPS_PROXY=https://user:pass@proxy.example.com:8080</pre>
				</div>
				<p style="color: var(--muted);">配置完后重启终端或运行 <code class="px-2 py-1 rounded bg-code">source ~/.zshrc</code>。</p>
			</div>
		</section>

		<section class="card rounded-[32px] p-8 shadow-card">
			<h2 class="font-display text-2xl font-semibold">防火墙规则</h2>
			<div class="mt-4 space-y-4 leading-8">
				<p>Claude Code 需要访问以下域名，确保防火墙放行：</p>
				<ul class="list-disc list-inside space-y-2 mt-4" style="color: var(--muted);">
					<li><code class="px-2 py-1 rounded bg-code">*.anthropic.com</code> — Anthropic API</li>
					<li><code class="px-2 py-1 rounded bg-code">*.claude.ai</code> — Claude 服务</li>
					<li><code class="px-2 py-1 rounded bg-code">*.amazonaws.com</code> — 如果用 Bedrock</li>
					<li><code class="px-2 py-1 rounded bg-code">*.googleapis.com</code> — 如果用 Vertex AI</li>
				</ul>
			</div>
		</section>

		<section class="card rounded-[32px] p-8 shadow-card">
			<h2 class="font-display text-2xl font-semibold">自签名证书</h2>
			<div class="mt-4 space-y-4 leading-8">
				<p>有些公司用自签名证书做中间人检查，需要把公司根证书加到系统信任列表：</p>
				<div class="mt-4 rounded-[24px] border p-6 font-mono text-sm overflow-x-auto" style="border-color: var(--line); background: var(--panel-strong);">
<pre># macOS - 把公司证书加到钥匙串
sudo security add-trusted-cert -d -r trustRoot \
  -k /Library/Keychains/System.keychain \
  /path/to/company-root.crt</pre>
				</div>
			</div>
		</section>

		<section class="card rounded-[32px] p-8 shadow-card">
			<h2 class="font-display text-2xl font-semibold">验证配置</h2>
			<div class="mt-4 space-y-4 leading-8">
				<p>在 Claude Code 里运行 <code class="px-2 py-1 rounded bg-code">/status</code> 命令，查看网络和代理配置是否正确。</p>
				<p style="color: var(--muted);">如果还有问题，检查代理日志、防火墙日志，或者联系公司 IT 部门。</p>
			</div>
		</section>

		<section class="card rounded-[32px] p-8 shadow-card">
			<h2 class="font-display text-2xl font-semibold">最后一句土话</h2>
			<div class="mt-4 space-y-4 leading-8">
				<p>企业网络配置就是给 Claude Code 办"通行证"。代理、防火墙、证书都配好了，它才能正常出门干活。</p>
				<p style="color: var(--muted);">配不好就找 IT 部门，别自己瞎折腾。</p>
			</div>
		</section>
	</article>
</Layout>
